<v-navigation-drawer :clipped="clipped" v-model="drawer" enable-resize-watcher>
    <v-toolbar flat>
        <v-list>
            <v-list-tile>
                <v-list-tile-title class="title">
                    Application
                </v-list-tile-title>
            </v-list-tile>
        </v-list>
    </v-toolbar>

    <v-divider></v-divider>

    <v-list dense class="pt-0">
        <v-list-tile
                v-for="item in items"
                :key="item.title"
        >
            <v-list-tile-action>
                <v-icon>{{ item.icon }}</v-icon>
            </v-list-tile-action>

            <v-list-tile-content>
                <v-list-tile-title>{{ item.title }}</v-list-tile-title>
            </v-list-tile-content>
        </v-list-tile>
    </v-list>
</v-navigation-drawer>
